      • setGetSupportNetWrapper

        public InitializeParam.InitializeParamBuilder setGetSupportNetWrapper(IWrapGetSupportNet getSupportNetWrapper)
        Set the network wrapper to query whether the device supports SOTER from server. You can set to null if you do not want to check from server
        参数:
        getSupportNetWrapper - the wrapper
        返回:
        the builder

      • setDistinguishSalt

        public InitializeParam.InitializeParamBuilder setDistinguishSalt(java.lang.String distinguishSalt)
        Set the salt added in authkey names in case you have some scenery to distinguish business scenes. You need it if you want to separate auth keys in different account.
        参数:
        distinguishSalt - the salt. The length of it must be less than 24
        返回:
        the builder

      • setScenes

        public InitializeParam.InitializeParamBuilder setScenes(int... scenes)
        Set the business scenes of your application. Each scene represents a pair of Auth Key. Scenes must be unique and non-null. The application should keep the scene values, and use the value instead of Auth Key name to operate on Auth Keys
        参数:
        scenes - the business scenes.
        返回:
        the builder

      • setCustomAppSecureKeyName

        public InitializeParam.InitializeParamBuilder setCustomAppSecureKeyName(java.lang.String customAppSecureKeyName)
        Set a custom app secure key name. Usually you do not need to set this. Just for compat former versions
        参数:
        customAppSecureKeyName - the custom key name
        返回:
        the builder

      • setSoterLogger

        public InitializeParam.InitializeParamBuilder setSoterLogger(ISoterLogger soterLogger)
        Set a log implement. You do not have to set it if you just use normal logcat for log printing
        参数:
        soterLogger - The log implement
        返回:
        the builder
